    - target: {fileID: 7241710067464557147, guid: 31bd6b4736421764897487b95984afcb, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: Visitors wander through the space, discover the orchestra in new arrangements,
        and experience how image, sound, and technology reinforce each other. In
        the Main Hall, a composition in which artificial intelligence plays a role
        is performed, among other pieces. Outside the hall, interactive installations
        and performances can be seen.
